Sales Manager, SEAT - Temperature (RMT/201403/04/SG)
Job ID
EPM-00007178
Country
Singapore
State/Province
Singapore
City
Singapore
Publish Start Date
Mar 25 2014
Job Level
Supervisor / Manager
|
Responsibilities:
Responsible for the strategy and execution of growth programs for the South East Asia & Taiwan (SEAT) Rosemount Temperature product line.
Drive strategies and tactics in concert with SEAT sales organization.
Support sales teams with technical, commercial and product strategies to grow market participation, price and meet the product group objectives.
Lead the training for new products, extensions and selling tools and tactics to the sales organization.
Ensure the SEAT sales organizations have the right tools and materials necessary to achieve consultative selling competency for Temperature solutions.
Represent SEAT market requirements, country specific opportunities and future product developmental needs to Product Marketing organization.
Work closely with all functional teams to ensure Temperature product strategies and growth alignment.
Requirements:
Degree in Engineering; MBA is an added advantage.
5 years experience in process automation or industrial technical marketing or sales.
Strong interpersonal and communication skills with good presentation skills.
Based in Singapore with requirement to travel 50% of the time.